Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.65,0:00:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't get away...this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.77,0:00:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.80,0:00:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- Right!\N- Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.87,0:00:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.83,0:00:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.85,0:00:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.00,0:00:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Kakashi Hatake...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.67,0:00:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I was planning to replace the hearts\NI lost with yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.72,0:00:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but I changed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.43,0:00:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I can get more hearts anytime I want,\Nafter all...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.86,0:00:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.38,0:00:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wind Style: Rasengan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.75,0:00:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Water Style: Ripping Torrent!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.82,0:00:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hurricane Vortex Jutsu!\N- Hurricane Vortex Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.95,0:01:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...we're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.95,0:01:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect timing...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.98,0:01:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the support...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.12,0:01:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura...Sai...and Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.97,0:01:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen you this beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.66,0:01:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.64,0:02:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This enemy...must be pretty strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.77,0:03:39.53,Title,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(698.438,585)}When You Curse Someone,\N{\i1}You Dig Your Own Grave\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.10,0:03:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,More strange people...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And he is pretty messed up already...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.63,0:03:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Shikamaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.45,0:03:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a little ways off\Nfighting the other enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I want two of you to\Nhead towards Shikamaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.89,0:04:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Preferably, a long-distance fighter\Nand a medic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.33,0:04:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.15,0:04:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.33,0:04:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai and Sakura follow Pakkun's lead\Nand support Shikamaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.05,0:04:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hah! What's this unorganized gang\Ntrying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Now there're more hearts for me\Nto choose from.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.83,0:04:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,From here on, this one's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.93,0:04:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.67,0:04:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We're off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto, I leave it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.95,0:05:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you... complete it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.50,0:05:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No... only about 50 percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.17,0:05:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.23,0:05:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, just watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.87,0:05:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto is not the same person\Nhe used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.87,0:05:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.80,0:05:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way... To go against an opponent\Nwho killed Asuma alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.63,0:05:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Shikamaru-kun... I mean,\NShikamaru going to be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.66,0:05:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Shikamaru is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He is...the most intelligent Shinobi\N{\i1}in the Land of Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Plus...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:06:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay... Well then, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh... He has absolutely no interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe he's a sub-captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.52,0:06:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that. It's difficult for him\Nto show any interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.07,0:06:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I bet he hates showing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He's trying really hard\Nto show disinterest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it...\NLady Tsunade, aren't you overrating him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.53,0:06:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I am still underrating him...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.14,0:06:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We recently received an official offer\Nfrom a Feudal Lord in the Land of Fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They want Shikamaru as a member of\Nthe Feudal Lord's personal guard division.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.11,0:07:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems Shikamaru's role as an \Nadministrator during the last Chunin exam
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.53,0:07:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,caught the attention of\None of the lord's assistants.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. The guard's division is like\Nthe Guardian Shinobi Twelve.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.67,0:07:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This means a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.21,0:07:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.13,0:07:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Then did Shikamaru...?\NAccept the offer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.57,0:07:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you rejected\Nthe Feudal Lord's offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.43,0:07:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.99,0:07:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a bad idea to experience\Nthe world outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:08:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I'd be here now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.79,0:08:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,if I had not been part of\Nthe Guardian Shinobi Twelve.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.72,0:08:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.26,0:08:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate tedious stuff\Nand that won't change in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.23,0:08:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.32,0:08:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because I'm concerned about Choji and Ino...\N and the other guys in the unit. And well, Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.53,0:08:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm just hanging around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...\NYou also have the Will of Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.69,0:08:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The Will of Fire...\NThe thing the Third used to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.05,0:08:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. It refers to the strong will\Nof wanting to protect this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing that noble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.94,0:08:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're concerned about them,\Nso you want to protect them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.57,0:09:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all Ninja of the Leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.99,0:09:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's bound to happen, even though\Nit's not really my thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.16,0:09:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The Will of Fire shines upon the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's what my dad told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll shine light on you someday.\NJust kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.63,0:09:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No need to worry about Shikamaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.13,0:09:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Besides, this is the battle to\N{\i1}avenge Asuma Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.03,0:09:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shikamaru should be fighting the enemy\N{\i1}with a perfect plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I can move...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I can move...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.63,0:10:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had believed in Lord Jashin,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,you may have gotten a helping hand\Nin your time of need.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.33,0:10:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'll believe in Lord Jashin from now on...\N to honor your reformation...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,As if I'd forgive you! Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.84,0:10:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care about his forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:10:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Shadow Pull Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.86,0:11:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have this much...Chakra left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.61,0:11:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.17,0:11:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.24,0:11:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Just watch...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.74,0:11:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?!\NWhen did you do this...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I had this trap prepared beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.11,0:12:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So he didn't just separate us on a whim,\N{\i1}but he purposely lured me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.06,0:12:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...this was all his plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,When you curse someone,\Nyou dig two holes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what that means?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.34,0:12:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If you curse to kill someone,\Nyou also get killed in retribution,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.02,0:12:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,that's why you need\Ntwo holes for the burial.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You cursed and killed my teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.82,0:12:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think I'll let you\Nget away free and easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.50,0:13:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This hole is your grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.90,0:13:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not gonna die...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.82,0:13:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if my body is dismembered\Ninto pieces and only my head remains,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.13,0:13:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I am going to drag myself out\Nand eat your throat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.63,0:13:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.49,0:13:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Deer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.12,0:13:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,These woods are a special place\Nin the Land of Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Our family is the only ones allowed in.\NNo one else comes here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.76,0:13:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Our family will always\Nkeep an eye on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.10,0:14:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You did a great job, Shikamaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.77,0:14:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.57,0:14:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,My Will of Fire...is now yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You, why...are you turning that on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:15:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Will of Fire...\Nthe will to protect our village.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good bye...Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Multi Shadow Clone Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.03,0:15:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Multiple Shadow Clones...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.36,0:15:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... You are the Nine-Tailed Jinchuriki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.10,0:15:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the situation\Nand the enemy's power?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.03,0:16:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy is two Akatsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.48,0:16:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,As I said before,\NShikamaru is fighting one of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.25,0:16:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and the other one is in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.50,0:16:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy has the power to split.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.95,0:16:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two masks on the shoulders\Nsplit from the torso.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.58,0:16:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Each mask has a separate heart\Nand moves independently.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.67,0:16:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He originally had five hearts.\NHe lost two and has only three now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.07,0:16:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've killed him twice already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to kill him three more times\Nto finish him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, he's an intermediate distance fighter and\N can use multiple Change in Chakra Natures.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.94,0:16:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No wonder you were\N{\i1}having a hard time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.47,0:16:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use charging in recklessly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.34,0:17:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You can only make Shadow Clones?\NYou can't beat me with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.76,0:17:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Based on his attack speed\N{\i1}and fighting style,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I need at least three Shadow Clones\N{\i1}to distract him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.69,0:17:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He gathered each clones' experience\N{\i1}and processed it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.35,0:17:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and based on that,\N{\i1}he formed a simulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.24,0:17:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His ability to use\N{\i1}Shadow Clones has advanced.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Multi Shadow Clone Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.96,0:17:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Three Shadow Clones...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.85,0:18:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's...that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What a...high pitched...Chakra!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What...are they...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried my best...\Nto build it up to here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,All right... To test its ability, let's collide it\Nwith my Rasengan. Get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.32,0:18:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! If we do that,\Nwhat's gonna happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.95,0:18:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If the Jutsu is near completion,\Nmy Rasengan will have no effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.74,0:18:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's do it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.36,0:19:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Fourth...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.67,0:19:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What...is that Jutsu...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.38,0:19:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I get hit by that...then I'm...\N{\i1}definitely doomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.60,0:20:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wind Style: Rasen Shuriken!
